*******************************************************************************
What's new in this version (1.2.5)
03/31/2020 (VincentWei)
	* ENHANCEMENT: Enable double bufferring.
	* ENHANCEMENT: Support for command to quit.
	* BUGFIXING: Use a button pressed flags to send button events.
    The fore implementation gave bad result for multiple buttons pressed status.

*******************************************************************************
What's new in this version (1.2.2)
12/15/2018 (VincentWei)
	* ENHANCEMENT: Add Virtual Video Layer (VVL) to simulate camera and video playback.
	* OPTIMIZATION: Use Cairo to render VFB and VVL.
	* ENHANCEMENT: Add vvlc-sample for VVL API.
	* CLEANUP: Fix compilation warnings of deprecated Gtk functions.

*******************************************************************************
What's new in this version (1.2.1)
10/24/2017 (VincentWei)
	* CLEANUP: Add X11 stuff in CMakeList.txt to generate correct ld options.

*******************************************************************************
